","type":"paragraph","text":"广播局、北京日报社、北京人民广播电台","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"9ff2a43904","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e083523f53","type":"paragraph","text":"上影、长影、西影、蛾影、珠影、八一厂、上科影、上美影、农","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"9ff2a43904","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"29d6bba83b","type":"paragraph","text":"影","index":9,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"9ff2a43904","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d5689817ba","type":"paragraph","text":"文化部办公厅、电影局、对外司、艺术局、教育司、文研所、政","index":10,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"9ff2a43904","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"936ce63d57","type":"paragraph","text":"研室、运办、北影、新影、科影、洗印厂","index":11,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"9ff2a43904","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ce15b9ddd6","type":"paragraph","text":"附：","index":12,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"9ff2a43904","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ba162ff741","type":"paragraph","text":"文化部关于恢复上映有邓小平同志形象的影片及有“批邓，反击右倾翻案风”词句的影片处理意见","index":13,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"9ff2a43904","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"00385d6f32","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九七七年七月二十三日）","index":14,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"9ff2a43904","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8fafead216","type":"paragraph","text":"根据党的十届三中全会精神，对于过去因为有邓小平问志形象而停映的影片和有“批邓，反击右倾翮案风”词句的影片，我们意见做如下处理：","index":15,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"9ff2a43904","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"94eb457aea","type":"paragraph","text":"一，有邓小平同志形象的影片，凡适合目前上映的（如《昔阳红似火》、《碧波传友情》等），即恢复上映。片中如有“四人帮”及其余党、亲信的镜头一律剪掉。","index":16,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"9ff2a43904","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"00996a5374","type":"paragraph","text":"二，凡适合目前上映而有“批邓，反击右倾翻案风”词句的影片，将该词句剪掉。","index":17,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"9ff2a43904","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f1305b2130","type":"paragraph","text":"妥否，请批示。","index":18,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"9ff2a43904","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}